<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/hello-world">Part I</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/hello-world-part-ii">Part II</a> | <span style="color: blue">Part III</span> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/hello-world-part-iv">Part IV</a> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p>
