<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Ah shit.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/hello-world-part-iii/grape_sad.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape_sad.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Three eyes blinked open from the head. Each twitched madly as it fought to focus on everything in the I/O Temple, especially MTF Kappa-10 laying on the ground.</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#9fbfdf; background:linear-gradient(#9fbfdf, #000); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p><sub>but me. i'm still classed as new i want to give you a brain. this is who i am, grape. i killed the WAN. i am the WAN. its still here because it stinks. the brain stinks, my friend.</sub></p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/hello-world-part-iii/hatbot_plain1.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="hatbot_plain1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
