</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Grape looked at Thorn. He shook his head in disappointment. Not at Thorn's ignorance, but at his own reluctance to utter that name. A name that reminded him of so much anger, frustration, and pity.</p>
